{{Quote|Generally my role is to produce any constructed background that you see behind the actors, whether it's an in-studio set or on location, including props and set dressing.|Gavin Bocquet|<ref>''[[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace Scrapbook]]''</ref>}}
'''Gavin Bocquet''' first worked in the ''[[Star Wars]]'' saga when he served as a draftsman on [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']]. He later served as production designer for five more [[George Lucas]] productions: the [[1992]] television series [[Wikipedia:The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles|''The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles'']], the [[1994]] feature film [[Wikipedia:Radioland Murders|''Radioland Murders'']], and the ''Star Wars'' [[prequel trilogy]] films.

Bocquet appears in the DVD documentary ''[[Within a Minute: The Making of Episode III]]''.

